Quote: ".. On former occasions when unemployment has been forced upon mill-hands scores have gone back to pick and shovel and unearthed sufficient gold to keep the wolf from the door. Such may be the case in the near future, although the majority of the young men employed in the bush have never had experience with the prospecting dish."
